<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfil do Usuário - Orkut</title>
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        inframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
       #profile-picture{
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
       }
        #container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        #profile-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        #profile-header img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #6b9cff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #6b9cff;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .profile-button {
            background-color: #6b9cff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .profile-button:hover {
            background-color: #476ad6;
        }

        #profile-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        #profile-footer a {
            color: #6b9cff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        #profile-footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <div id="profile-header">
            <img  src="https://i.ibb.co/KxPK6m0/Carlinhos.png" alt="Profile Picture">
            <h1><%= user.name %></h1>
            <p>E-mail: <%= user.email %></p>
            <a href="#" class="profile-button">Adicionar aos Amigos</a>
            <a href="#" class="profile-button">Enviar Mensagem</a>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Interesses:</strong> Tecnologia, Música, Esportes</p>
        <p><strong>Sobre Mim:</strong> Olá! Sou um usuário do Orkut, adoro conhecer novas pessoas e fazer amizades. Sinta-se à vontade para me adicionar como amigo!</p>
        <div id="profile-footer">
            <a href="#">Editar Perfil</a> |
            <a href="/users">Usuários</a> |
            <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
        </div>
        <div id="profile-picture">

        <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_Appw2sGt9A?si=EwgnoC_SDvLdBoz4" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
</body>
</html>